    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen remains in showroom condition, featuring flawless coachwork and a pristine interior that reflects its meticulous ownership history. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a definitive acquisition for the most discerning driver.",
